object.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT basicpolicy_stg.SystemId,basicpolicy_stg.Id, basicpolicy_stg.PolicyNumber, basicpolicy_stg.StatusCd, basicpolicy_stg.CarrierCd,basicpolicy_stg.TransactionCd,basicpolicy_stg.InceptionDt, basicpolicy_stg.EffectiveDt, basicpolicy_stg.ExpirationDt, basicpolicy_stg.CancelDt, case when len(basicpolicy_stg.policyversion)='1' then concat('00',basicpolicy_stg.policyversion)
             when len(basicpolicy_stg.policyversion)='2' then concat('0',basicpolicy_stg.policyversion)
             else basicpolicy_stg.policyversion end as policyversion, basicpolicy_stg.QuoteNumber, basicpolicy_stg.ProviderRef,basicpolicy_stg.ApplicationNumber,basicpolicy_stg.ManualRenewalInd,basicpolicy_stg.ProgramCd,basicpolicy_stg.Tier,basicpolicy_stg.PayPlanCd,basicpolicy_stg.InspectionOrderedDt, basicpolicy_stg.SubTypeCd
,basicpolicy_stg.ControllingStateCd,basicpolicy_stg.ShellPolicyInd, basicpolicy_stg.RenewalPolicyRef
,basicpolicy_stg.IsMigrated
,Insured_stg.InspectionContact
,Insured_stg.InspectionContactNumber
,emailinfo_stg.EmailAddr 
FROM
 dbo.basicpolicy_stg (nolock) basicpolicy_stg 
 LEFT JOIN dbo.Insured_stg Insured_stg (nolock) ON basicpolicy_stg.SystemId = Insured_stg.SystemId AND basicpolicy_stg.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
  AND Insured_stg.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
  AND basicpolicy_stg.ShellPolicyInd IS NULL
LEFT JOIN dbo.emailinfo_stg emailinfo_stg  ON basicpolicy_stg.SystemId = emailinfo_stg.SystemId
  AND basicpolicy_stg.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
  AND emailinfo_stg.CMMContainer = 'Policy'
  AND basicpolicy_stg.ShellPolicyInd IS NULL
  AND emailinfo_stg.EmailTypeCd = 'InsuredEmail' ;

object.customQuery:
SELECT Line_Stg.ParentId        as ParentId,
       Line_Stg.CMMContainer    as CMMContainer,
       Line_Stg.LineCd          as LineCd,
       Line_Stg.NumHouseAutoRec as NumHouseAutoRec,
       Line_Stg.NumOfYouthInexp as NumOfYouthInexp,
       Line_Stg.CoverageTypeCd  as CoverageTypeCd,
       Line_Stg.SystemId        as SystemId
FROM dbo.Line_Stg
WHERE Line_Stg.cmmcontainer = 'Policy'
